text.tspan: Time spent on travel, per day, men vs women
Average minutes spent on travel per day, by sex (20-74). Estimates come from time use surveys and include one
weekday and one weekend day distributed over the year. Travel includes commutes and trips connected with all
kinds of activities, except travel during working hours.
Source: European Commission (2004) - How Europeans spend their time - Everyday life of men and women - Data 1998-2002
